divs: Sighting DetailsSmoking a cigarette in yard. Thought I was looking at a star, till it started to move. Thought it was a plane but there were no visible flashing lights, could not have been a meteor because it never burnt out and the flightpath was too erratic. Was excited to see my first actual ufo sighting. Lost sight when it flew straight up and left 3 perfect rings of clouds.
Summary: Starlike object seemed to follow dark clouds, flew higher than a plane and very fast.
